item.title: Client help
item.dc:creator: @Mr_Despair Mr. Despair
item.description:
@Mr_Despair wrote:

Make a .batch and put this into it, or adjust it to your server specifications.

@echo off start javaw -Xmx500m -cp .;Theme.jar Gui exit

You haven’t set your environmental variables correctly, there’s a plethora of tutorials on how to do this in Server Tutorials

Oh and if you are a masters in programming you should of known how to this.
